dct_title_s: Strategical map of part of Korea and Manchuria
dct_description_sm: Shows boundaries between Manchuria and northern Korea, Mongolia and Siberia at the end of the Russo-Japanese War. Indicates railroads and submarine cables. Relief shown by shading. "Drawn by Chas. L. Hoopes." Inset is continuation of main map. Inset: southern Korea, Korea Strait, northern Japan. Scale [ca. 1:3,960,000].
dct_creator_sm: United States. War Department. General Staff
United States. War Department General Staff
